// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P2949863910" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Superpyrite Amulet</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The Carnival of Shadows has been rather quiet lately, and this note you just found might explain why:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>'Antonio, word on the street is that the Carnival is accepting members.  Check it out, you don't need to wear one of those dumb masks.  All you gotta do is wear this amulet they give you made outta - get this - SUPER pyrite!  We gotta get in on some of this action!'</scale></font></color><br><br> Indeed.  Perhaps you need to do the same... while all of these potential crime-doers are milling about at the same time."
// Answer Text :
"P2950349708" "VILLAIN: Use the Carnival event to take out everyone!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


