// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P3452270605" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Tortured Scream</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>As you're doing your part to eradicate evil from this world, you are suddenly assaulted by a blood-curdling screaming... emanating from your mind:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>PLEEEEEEASEEEEEE!!!  Come help me... help ussss... We of the Circle of Thorns have bound a being... too great for even us... our souls have been stripped... follow my pain... before I was bound, I wrote down how... how to stop this... helppp.... </scale></font></color><br><br> Once again, the Circle has tampered with forces beyond their control.  But they weren't counting on someone like you to come stop them..."
// Answer Text :
"P2290843805" "VILLAIN: Annihilate those who would deal with dark forces!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


