// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P3809877047" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Failed Ransom</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You come across a briefcase filled with unmarked, foreign currency.  Inside you also find a note:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Androleve, I am trusting you will do job smoothly.  You give money only when my brother is safely in your hands.  If Arachnos has harmed single hair of Dmitrev, then I swear we will bring hammer down on them like bugs! -  Gorzky</scale></font></color><br><br>It seems you've come across a hostage exchange involving a sizeable amount of money.  Not only that, it looks like it's involving some foreign agency and Arachnos... and a lot of threats. <br><br>What was that saying?  The enemy of my enemy is my friend..."
// Answer Text :
"P1156030309" "VILLAIN: Make sure this ransom fails."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
