// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P465721175" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Merlin's Magical Menagerie</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a rough cut of an episode of the popular children's show involving magic and puppets, Merlin's Magical Menagerie.  This episode features a cameo of Desdemona, the former demon-binder now turned 'hero'.  This rough cut doesn't appear to be edited yet, so it still contains all the errors that happen during filming:<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Crying Child: [crying] It's going to hurt me. - Desdemona: [hugging the child] No, sweetheart, I've made it go away.  It can't hurt you. - Crying Child: Thank you, Ms. Desdemona.  I see what you mean that summoning demons is no joke! - Desdemona - [pointing at the other children] And safety is no laughing matter. [children wave at the camera, cut to credits]</scale></font></color><br><br>Desdemona is now doing children's public service announcements?  The same woman who directed the Viscount of Ruination to destroy an orphanage just to spite the heroes of Paragon City? She's convinced your peers that she's turned a new leaf, and now she's working on the kids?  Unfortunately for her, in your hands is the proof she's evil.  Well, after you're done editing the tape, that is."
// Answer Text :
"P1575491969" "VILLAIN: 'Correct' the episode to show what you know is true"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


